text: "Good Morning" is a 2009 song made by American rapper Chamillionaire, The song was going to be the first single from Chamillionaire's studio album, Venom but in 2011 the album was stopped because Chamillionaire and Universal parted ways. A music video was made on November 10, 2009. The single was at number 40 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart. ==Track listing== ;Digital Single ==Chart positions== Chart (2009) Peak position ==References== Category:2009 songs Category:Chamillionaire songs Category:Songs written by Chamillionaire
